When there’s a noteworthy notification (that is: one
that you should be highlighted about — not simply a
random update), a little notification speck shows up
• Packages you’re responsible for show up in a stream
• There is activity on bugs you’ve pariticpated in
• Discussions you’re a part of have activity
Notifications will not show up for:
• A page prompting the speck is loaded
• Activity is acknowledged (when an issue seen in
a bug tracker, even if not on Hubs)
